Perform and write truffle installation steps:
1. Install node js
2. Install truffle: CMD —> npm install truffle
3. Verify truffle: CMD —> truffle version
4. Create truffle project: CMD —> mkdir MyProject
						cd MyProject
5. Initialize truffle in directory: CMD —> truffle init
6. In contracts folder, create a simple contract, named SimpeStorage.sol
Code:
// SPDX-License-Identifier: MIT
pragma solidity ^0.8.0;

contract SimpleStorage {

    uint public data;

    function setData(uint _data) public {
        data = _data;
    }

    function getData() public view returns(uint) {
        return data;
    }
}

7. Save it and compile the contract: CMD —> truffle compile

